276
00:30:20,490 --> 00:30:22,220
What are you saying?

277
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:26,850
Sounds like you're saying the culprit might have been framed...

278
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:32,320
The culprit left Im Do Sool in a not so fatal state...

279
00:30:32,320 --> 00:30:34,720
