280
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:37,310
Why would he do that?

281
00:30:40,780 --> 00:30:41,810
Pain...

282
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:49,790
The culprit wanted the victim to watch his family get murdered.

283
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:53,770
This murder was for revenge.

284
00:30:55,610 --> 00:30:56,670
Director Yeo.

285
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,780
