317
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:18,580
No! Only debt collectors.

318
00:33:18,580 --> 00:33:22,860
What are these numbers?

319
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,900
She's so strange.

320
00:33:25,900 --> 00:33:28,580
Her daughter is old enough to know her numbers.

321
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:31,380
I don't know why she wrote these numbers on the stairs.

322
00:33:43,010 --> 00:33:48,440
No usage of the transportation card or call history after the crime...

323
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:53,910
She didn't meet anyone either...

324
00:33:59,700 --> 00:34:03,890
