342
00:38:05,930 --> 00:38:06,780
Yes, Senior.

343
00:38:23,270 --> 00:38:24,160
The account book?

344
00:38:24,160 --> 00:38:27,750
Of course, I brought it.

345
00:38:47,390 --> 00:38:48,880
The rest is in here.

346
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:51,820
Forget the money.

347
00:38:59,520 --> 00:39:00,720
