381
00:42:49,190 --> 00:42:51,700
What are you saying?

382
00:42:51,700 --> 00:42:54,640
Even though his job was shady,
he lived an honest life!

383
00:42:54,640 --> 00:42:56,000
You motherfuc-

384
00:42:57,140 --> 00:42:58,680
Motherfucker?

385
00:42:58,680 --> 00:42:59,650
Motherfuc-

386
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:03,910
