391
00:43:28,080 --> 00:43:30,960
This is the wine that the criminal drank.

392
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:33,150
Looking at Im Do Sool's wine collection...

393
00:43:33,150 --> 00:43:35,910
Most of the labels were ridiculously expensive.

394
00:43:35,910 --> 00:43:37,900
Should I say he had vulgar taste?

395
00:43:39,260 --> 00:43:43,050
If he had to choose one wine out of his entire collection...

396
00:43:43,680 --> 00:43:45,060
It would be this one.

397
00:43:47,680 --> 00:43:49,920
1982 Cheval Blanc.

398
00:43:51,260 --> 00:43:55,050
Is it a coincidence that the culprit chose to drink this specific wine?

399
00:43:57,320 --> 00:43:59,420
You can fool one's eyes.

400
00:44:00,150 --> 00:44:02,460
But you can't fool one's taste.

401
00:44:02,460 --> 00:44:03,830
Taste?

402
00:44:04,580 --> 00:44:06,380
We've been doing this the wrong way.

403
00:44:06,980 --> 00:44:10,030
Kang Jong Yoon isn't the criminal.
He was framed.

404
00:44:10,030 --> 00:44:12,090
And he's looking for the real killer right now.

405
00:44:13,400 --> 00:44:15,680
The one wanting revenge against Im Do Sool...

406
00:44:16,690 --> 00:44:19,200
The one who likes Cheval Blanc...

407
00:44:20,670 --> 00:44:21,950
Wait.

408
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:23,930
So...

409
00:44:23,930 --> 00:44:28,580
So you're saying it wasn't that gambler but someone else?

410
00:44:32,730 --> 00:44:35,420
Kang Jong Yoon is finding the real killer?

411
00:44:40,390 --> 00:44:44,390
Whether it's Cheval or bullshit or whatever-

412
00:44:44,390 --> 00:44:47,270
My taste is soju so I'll go my own way.

413
00:44:48,130 --> 00:44:54,400
While you write your novel, I'll be investigating the medical facilities.

414
00:45:00,130 --> 00:45:01,820
Kang Jong Yoon is calling!

415
00:45:02,270 --> 00:45:04,070
He wants to talk to the Detective in charge.

416
00:46:53,880 --> 00:46:55,980
Kang Jong Yoon is calling!

417
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:57,860
He wants to talk to the Detective in charge.

418
00:47:15,870 --> 00:47:18,230
This is Yeo Ji Hoon from the Special Affairs Team.

419
00:47:18,230 --> 00:47:20,050
<i>It's him!
The bastard who called me!</i>

420
00:47:21,300 --> 00:47:23,980
I thought that bastard was dead.

421
00:47:23,980 --> 00:47:27,120
<i>The man I met that night wasn't Im Do Sool!</i>

422
00:47:27,880 --> 00:47:29,260
Kang Jong Yoon.

423
00:47:29,260 --> 00:47:31,360
Right now, you're wanted as the prime suspect.

424
00:47:32,270 --> 00:47:34,120
If you want to prove your innocence, come to the station-

425
00:47:34,120 --> 00:47:36,980
You don't think I know that you'll just arrest me?

426
00:47:37,890 --> 00:47:40,110
I'm telling you that the bastard framed me!

427
00:47:44,420 --> 00:47:46,880
I'll record this conversation so tell me in detail.

428
00:47:51,420 --> 00:47:53,020
Okay.

429
00:47:53,020 --> 00:47:53,990
Start.

430
00:47:55,100 --> 00:47:57,110
<i>I went to the house...</i>

431
00:47:58,300 --> 00:48:00,460
<i>That bastard let me in...</i>

432
00:48:00,460 --> 00:48:03,060
<i>I thought it was his house.</i>

433
00:48:06,560 --> 00:48:09,350
Good work today.
Have a seat.

434
00:48:19,100 --> 00:48:20,660
Have a drink.

435
00:48:24,590 --> 00:48:25,870
Thank you.

436
00:48:37,130 --> 00:48:39,680
