My daughter likes to play around.

441
00:48:57,350 --> 00:48:59,250
I'm sure you know how 4 year olds can get.

442
00:48:59,250 --> 00:49:01,370
Tell me about your family.

443
00:49:01,370 --> 00:49:03,320
Do I really need to say?

444
00:49:03,320 --> 00:49:05,890
You don't have to if you don't want to.

445
00:49:12,200 --> 00:49:14,410
Can I have another drink?

446
00:49:26,220 --> 00:49:28,640
Today is my daughter's birthday.

447
00:49:28,640 --> 00:49:30,880
The last time I saw her was when she was two.

448
00:49:30,880 --> 00:49:32,610
She should be 6 now.

449
00:49:33,590 --> 00:49:36,530
You should at least call.

450
00:49:37,950 --> 00:49:40,490
I've given up on seeing her in real life.

451
00:49:41,310 --> 00:49:44,050
When I think about her and my wife...

452
00:49:44,900 --> 00:49:47,170
Someone like me should die.

453
00:49:47,170 --> 00:49:49,220
We should go to hell.

454
00:49:51,600 --> 00:49:53,780
I should've cut my wrists back then.

455
00:49:54,340 --> 00:49:56,340
There's no point in cutting your wrists.

456
00:49:57,650 --> 00:49:59,860
If you're going to cut them, you should cut them here.

457
00:50:16,740 --> 00:50:20,270
If I hire you for 2 days, is 7 enough?

458
00:50:20,270 --> 00:50:21,650
That's plenty.

459
00:50:21,650 --> 00:50:24,440
I initially invested in one week.

460
00:50:24,440 --> 00:50:26,390
But something came up.

461
00:50:40,140 --> 00:50:43,040
