466
00:51:01,420 --> 00:51:03,170
Nobody.

467
00:51:04,320 --> 00:51:05,830
I don't know.

468
00:51:06,460 --> 00:51:08,320
Hey Kang Jong Yoon!

469
00:51:08,320 --> 00:51:11,150
If you already got the money,
why did you go back?

470
00:51:11,150 --> 00:51:12,490
Especially at dawn?!

471
00:51:12,490 --> 00:51:14,910
Why don't you come here and draw the montage then, you bastard?!

472
00:51:14,910 --> 00:51:16,640
<i>That-</i>

473
00:51:16,640 --> 00:51:18,240
