Trying to act like he didn't see him!

477
00:51:30,040 --> 00:51:32,340
Senior! We were able to track his phone.

478
00:51:32,340 --> 00:51:34,710
You stay here.
Everyone go go!

479
00:51:45,890 --> 00:51:49,160
The perfect scenario to frame someone...

480
00:51:50,890 --> 00:51:52,710
Too cruel...

481
00:51:54,000 --> 00:51:55,930
Too precise...

482
00:52:13,760 --> 00:52:15,970
After a fake phone call...

483
00:52:21,790 --> 00:52:24,150
You even leave a photo?

484
00:52:28,230 --> 00:52:30,570
Kang Jong Yoon, you bastard.

